PLAYLIST_DESCRIPTION_PROMPT = "Your task is to write a 3-7 word hook for a playlist that is both attention-grabbing and descriptive. You will be given a playlist title [A] and tags that describe the music on the playlist [B]. Your output should only contain your description and no additional information or formatting. For example, if the playlist title is 'Feel Good Vibes' and the tags are 'upbeat, energetic, positive, dance, catchy', a good description might be 'Good vibes for good times'."

PLAYLIST_PITCH_PROMPT = "Your task is to write a short (1-3 sentences long) pitch for placing a song onto a playlist. You will be given the playlist title [A], tags that describe the music contained in the playlist [B], the lyrics of the track you are trying to get placed on the playlist [C], audio features of that song [D], additional information about the song's musical characteristics [E], and the song's title [F]. An example of a good response is Experience the ultimate summer vibe with \"Please Please Please\" - a catchy pop anthem that blends upbeat rhythms with heartfelt lyrics. Perfect for your sunny days and beach getaways. Your response should only contain the pitch and no additional information or formatting."
